headline: Labcorp CFO Glenn Eisenberg Announces Plans to Retire
summary: Labcorp (NYSE: LH), a global leader of innovative and comprehensive laboratory services, announced today that Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer (CFO) Glenn Eisenberg will retire from the company and Julia Wang will join on December 2, 2024, as Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer.
